SSH -  allow secure shell login, remote program execution, simple file sharing. Replace Telnet and rlogin.
SSH protocol - OpenSSH. OpenSSH client program is ssh and the server is sshd.

SSH Benefits.
- Encrypts your password and all other session data.
- Tunnels other network connection.(Tunneling(port forwarding). Is a protocol that allows the secure movement of data from one network to another.)
- Uses Keys for host authentication.

SSH Disadvantage.
- remote host public key are not got in a secure way.
